skdetail:

Invocation Name: key locator
des: We've all been there, the frustrating and frantic to rush to find one's keys. Key Locator will give you a random place to look for your keys, maybe it won't help but maybe it'll jog your memory in just the right way! If nothing else the Skill features calming photos (on compatible devices) to take your mind off being late for work.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
